/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n還番我谷左五日既精兵俾我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d79cc8a157a0ada1481d6d5c4d339199bb29371","tid":939431,"uid":93060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:59:59.000Z","msg":"呢段先岩 <br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n<br />\n平時一大早起身見到湖琳個mv<br />\n<br />\n我已經&quot;動L&quot;左既小弟弟就想向佢發炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但為求對湖琳既尊重<br />\n<br />\n於是我特登谷左五日唔打飛機<br />\n<br />\n諗住一炮過射俾湖琳，俾佢做facial<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日已經谷左五日如箭在弦既小弟弟再忍唔住啦<br />\n<br />\n一開電視，湖琳已經係到ready 緊我d面部護理&quot;精&quot;華&quot;液&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我用手將小弟弟好似shotgun咁狂chok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就黎顏射佢既時候...你老母<br />\n<br />\n電視突然轉左做公碩良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我幾億精兵又忍唔住出左一半，收唔撚番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是一路嗌：哎呀，仆街啦，你老母，呀...呀...呀...呀...呀...<br />\n<br />\n就咁我幾億子彈射左落公碩良塊面到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街，而家仲好撚興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，早知下次定住個畫面先射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n還番我谷左五日既精兵俾我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746ae268c0c714f43dcd19d5c4e60fd98ebcdb